text: "Bilar" is the Swedish word for 'automobiles' (Singular 'Bil'). Bilar can refer to: * Bilar, Bohol, a municipality in the province of Bohol, Philippines * Bilär, a village in Republic of Tatarstan, Russia ** Bilars, a medieval Turkic tribe, founders of Bilär * Elvillar/Bilar, a town and municipality in Basque Country, Spain * Bilar, Swedish title of Cars (film) * 'Ahlgrens bilar' or Ahlgrens Cars, A popular Swedish Candy
title: Bilar
